Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.94,0:01:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.02,0:01:52.15,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.15,0:01:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bibi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.98,0:01:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang terjadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.05,0:02:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Hei! Kami butuh brankar di sini!\N- Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.42,0:02:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Putriku ada di bawah sana!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.97,0:02:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sia-sia saja! Tidak bisa dipindahkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.39,0:02:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada waktu untuk itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.68,0:02:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat! Tinggalkan saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.89,0:02:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Nak! Kau sedang apa?\NCepatlah berevakuasi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.19,0:02:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasukan Ostania akan segera tiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.86,0:02:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ostania?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.27,0:02:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi katanya tak akan ada perang...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.53,0:02:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah kau masih hidup!\NApa yang kau lakukan di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.49,0:02:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.24,0:02:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau terluka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.12,0:02:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kurasa
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.37,0:02:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}helmku menyelamatkan nyawaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.38,0:02:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita harus segera pulang dan berkemas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.59,0:02:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari pergi ke rumah paman Ibu di Kielberg.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.46,0:02:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.34,0:03:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak mau. Sekolahku bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.80,0:03:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, besok ada festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.34,0:03:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini bukan saatnya untuk itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.60,0:03:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tak mengerti?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.29,0:03:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Meski pasukan Westalis\Nsudah berusaha keras,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.88,0:03:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kota Luwen di timur sudah direbut.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.26,0:03:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Pada tanggal 18, Perdana Menteri Adner...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.64,0:03:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}- Orang dewasa memang pembohong.\N- ...adakan konferensi pers sehubungan{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.10,0:03:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}- dengan banyaknya korban sipil.\N- Katanya kita tak akan berperang.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.27,0:03:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Bahkan para orang penting berkata{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.98,0:03:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}- kedua pihak akur berkat pakta itu.\N- Tidak bisa dimaafkan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.77,0:03:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Ayah juga.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.07,0:04:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Ayah berjanji akan pergi ke festival\Nbersamaku setelah pulang.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.69,0:04:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tapi dia tak pernah kembali.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.78,0:04:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Sebenarnya, aku juga seorang pembohong.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku berbohong untuk dapat sepuluh dalc\Ndan tak pernah mengembalikannya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Setelah Ayah pulang,\Naku akan memberi tahu kebenarannya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.83,0:04:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku harus berkata jujur pada dia.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.17,0:04:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.51,0:04:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.76,0:04:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan khawatir.\NSemua akan baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu, aku mau pulang ke Luwen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayah mungkin akan pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau bermain\Ndengan Jenderal dan yang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.03,0:04:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hebat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.75,0:05:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semoga Ibu senang\Njika kubawa ini pulang untuk makan malam.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.21,0:05:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, akhir-akhir ini\Nkami tak bisa makan sampai kenyang.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serangan udara!\NSegera pergi ke tempat berlindung!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.10,0:05:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.22,0:05:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat! Ke sini!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo, Nak! Masuk!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.06,0:05:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Tunggu, aku harus pulang...\N- Cepat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.40,0:05:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masuk dan sisakan tempat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.78,0:05:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Buat anak itu diam!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ostania sialan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.66,0:05:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.70,0:05:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah berhenti? Sudah berakhir?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.21,0:05:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan dibuka, Nak!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.75,0:05:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bodoh! Kembali ke dalam!\NSituasinya masih berbahaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.27,0:05:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rumahnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.94,0:06:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak mungkin...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak... Ibu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.23,0:06:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.97,0:06:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku bahkan tak ingat{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}berapa tahun aku menjalani hidup\Nbagai tikus jalanan setelah itu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.43,0:06:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Semua yang kucintai direnggut dariku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.89,0:06:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Yang tertinggal di dunia ini\Nhanya hal-hal yang kubenci.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Itu sudah menjadi cukup alasan{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.49,0:06:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}bagiku untuk mengangkat senjata.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lorand Spoofy dari Luwen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.16,0:07:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau benar-benar cukup umur\Nuntuk wajib militer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya. Usiaku 18 tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.29,0:07:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kartu keluargaku hilang saat perang.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.25,0:07:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Itu bohong.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.38,0:07:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, kita harus apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Berapa banyak mayat,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}ribuan atau puluhan ribu,\Nyang harus aku kumpulkan{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}agar bisa melihat matahari terbit\Ndari cakrawala?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Jebakan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu! Berhenti! Jangan tembak!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau prajurit Ostania?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.83,0:07:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gawat, ada prajurit Westalis!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.09,0:07:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bawa senjata?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.09,0:07:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak! Aku tak bersenjata! Aku menyerah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.76,0:07:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku kabur! Aku sudah muak!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku tersesat dan sudah berada\Ndi gunung ini selama dua hari...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.43,0:08:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kumohon! Bagilah makananmu denganku!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.39,0:08:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sia-sia saja memberi makanan\Npada orang yang sudah mati.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.23,0:08:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Matilah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.81,0:08:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku belum pernah berpacaran!\NAku tak boleh mati di sini!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.61,0:08:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Ada apa dengannya?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.62,0:08:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau boleh ambil satu batang rokok.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.62,0:08:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Ternyata, aku bisa melihat musuhku\Nsebagai seorang manusia.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.38,0:08:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada eksperimen menarik\Nyang dilakukan di universitas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka menunjukkan video Pria A\Nyang ditampar pada para peserta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.13,0:08:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Kau bicara soal apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Apa dia memahami situasi dia sekarang?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.56,0:08:46.02,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}{\i1}Otak mereka berempati terhadap rasa sakit
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.56,0:08:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan mereka merasa tak nyaman.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.02,0:08:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Pada dasarnya, secara alami,\Nmanusia cenderung menghindari kekerasan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.57,0:08:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tapi{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.36,0:08:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}mereka menunjukkan video itu lagi,\Ntapi kali ini,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.53,0:08:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}dijelaskan bahwa Pria A ditampar\Nkarena selingkuh dari pacarnya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.24,0:09:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kau tahu apa yang terjadi?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Otak para peserta menunjukkan\Ntanda-tanda kesenangan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengerikan, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.33,0:09:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Otak manusia\Nbisa dipengaruhi dengan mudah,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.75,0:09:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}hanya dengan menyebut sesuatu secara\Nberbeda, terlepas itu benar atau tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.55,0:09:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seram, 'kan? Tapi aku tak tahu\Nseberapa akurat statistiknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Intinya apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.80,0:09:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah ini bodoh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.97,0:09:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perang Timur-Barat ini pada dasarnya\Nadalah akibat dari kegagalan diplomasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.27,0:09:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa warga biasa seperti kita
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}harus membereskan kekacauan mereka?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.73,0:09:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka buat kita saling benci\Ndemi kepentingan sendiri,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.24,0:09:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}lalu kita bertarung sampai mati.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.53,0:09:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini hal paling tak berguna di dunia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.66,0:09:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian, warga Ostania,\Nyang memulai perang ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.16,0:09:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di pihak kami, kami diberi tahu
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.33,0:09:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bahwa kalian duluan yang ganggu kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.46,0:09:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katanya pengeboman pertama di Luwen
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.46,0:09:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dilakukan sendiri oleh Barat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.59,0:09:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada yang bilang bahwa Barat\Nmeminta negara pihak ketiga
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.05,0:10:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}menghasut pasukan Ostania di balik layar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.43,0:10:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu propaganda yang kalian sebar\Nuntuk membenarkan tindakan kalian!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.31,0:10:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.23,0:10:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi prajurit pangkat rendah seperti kita\Ntak akan pernah tahu kebenarannya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.65,0:10:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pada hari itu, di pengeboman itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.94,0:10:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}semua orang,\Ntermasuk teman-temanku, tewas!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itulah kebenarannya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.86,0:10:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami juga mengalami itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.36,0:10:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.03,0:10:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kalian jahat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.95,0:10:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kalian merenggut segalanya dariku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pernah lihat orang Ostania\Nberbuat keji secara langsung?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.38,0:10:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Sudah! Aku sudah melihatnya berulang kali!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.17,0:10:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Jadi, kubuat mereka\Nmengalami takdir yang sama.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.30,0:10:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Untuk membalas dendam semua orang...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa mereka mengejarku?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.56,0:10:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka menemukanku karena kau menembak!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:10:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sial! Aku tak boleh tertangkap di sini!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.49,0:11:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dah! Tapi terima kasih untuk rokoknya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.74,0:11:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sial!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.05,0:11:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Apa...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.68,0:11:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Apa yang kulakukan?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.43,0:11:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kudengar kau ditugaskan\Ndi garis belakang karena luka-lukamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.81,0:11:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasti menyenangkan.\NAku sangat iri, Lorand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.23,0:11:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau nyaris tewas, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.53,0:11:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.33,0:11:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau Penasihat, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.54,0:11:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jenderal?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.75,0:11:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kopral?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.21,0:11:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mayor?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.30,0:12:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Sudah kuduga!\N- Itu Penasihat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.26,0:12:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak mungkin! Kau serius?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.01,0:12:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami mencarimu, tapi tak ketemu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami sungguh mengira kau sudah mati!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.81,0:12:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah kau masih hidup!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.85,0:12:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kini kau sangat tinggi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.27,0:12:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.44,0:12:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau menangis?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.99,0:12:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.03,0:12:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau masih seperti pengecut, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.87,0:12:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka bilang
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.95,0:12:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}gudang itu yang dibom pertama kali.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.79,0:12:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kukira kalian tewas
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.75,0:12:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}gara-gara aku,\Nkarena aku menemukan tempat itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.50,0:12:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan aku sangat marah pada diriku sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.13,0:12:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pada hari itu,\Nkau pergi karena suatu alasan, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk membantu festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.22,0:12:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar. Jadi, kami mengejarmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tepat setelah itu, gudangnya meledak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.19,0:12:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi beberapa teman sekelas kita\Nbenar-benar tewas.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.61,0:13:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakakku juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.90,0:13:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, Penasihat,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.65,0:13:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku bersyukur kau baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.66,0:13:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari jatuhkan Ostania bersama-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.53,0:13:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kali ini, kita semua\Nmenjadi prajurit Westalis.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.25,0:13:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kita cuma prajurit biasa,\Nbelum ada yang jadi kopral.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang benar saja! Kau sudah menjadi sersan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.63,0:13:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kebetulan saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Para perwira yang menjadi seniorku\Nsudah gugur.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.01,0:13:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf sudah bicara santai denganmu, Sersan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.26,0:13:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hentikan. Aku tak peduli soal itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.94,0:13:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya mau
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.69,0:13:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}berkumpul lagi dengan kalian,\Nseperti biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.19,0:13:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada waktu luang akhir pekan ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.32,0:13:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada restoran enak di kota sebelah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Unit kami akan pergi malam ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.20,0:13:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka mengirim kami\Nuntuk Kampanye Roberts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.66,0:13:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.83,0:14:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Lorand!\NBawa bawang bombainya ke sini!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.84,0:14:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Lorand? Tapi namamu...\N- Itu nama panggilan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.09,0:14:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pokoknya, kabari aku\Nkalau kalian sudah kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.76,0:14:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Jangan lupa, ya?\N- Oke!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.47,0:14:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Sampai jumpa!\N- Sampai jumpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.52,0:14:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tidak lama setelah itu, kudengar{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.81,0:14:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}mereka dikirim{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.94,0:14:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}untuk sebuah misi\Nyang terburu-buru dan gegabah.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.52,0:14:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Yang kembali hanyalah\Nketiga tanda pengenal militer mereka.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Jika tahu soal misi itu,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.91,0:14:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}bisakah kuhentikan mereka sebelum pergi?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.83,0:14:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Jika tahu soal rencana musuh kami,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.41,0:14:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}bisakah kuhentikan misinya\Nsebelum itu dilaksanakan?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.12,0:14:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tidak. Aku tak punya kuasa seperti itu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.92,0:14:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku pun tak tahu cara mencapai\Nposisi dengan kuasa sebesar itu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.59,0:14:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku tak tahu apa pun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.18,0:14:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku tak pernah tahu apa pun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.47,0:14:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku saja tak tahu\Nalasan di balik perang ini.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.18,0:15:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku berasumsi perang tak akan terjadi,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.31,0:15:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}aku berasumsi semua orang\Ntewas dalam pengeboman itu,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.77,0:15:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}aku membenci musuh\Ntanpa mempertanyakan apa pun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.36,0:15:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku mengangkat senjata\Ntanpa mempertanyakan apa pun,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.61,0:15:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}dan mematuhi negaraku\Ntanpa mempertanyakan apa pun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.83,0:15:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Ketidaktahuan{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}sungguh lemah{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}dan jahat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dunia ini bagai bawang bombai raksasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.64,0:15:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya akumulasi\Ndari berlapis-lapis kebohongan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.64,0:15:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tak bisa mengupas lapisan itu\Ntanpa meneteskan air mata.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.94,0:15:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.56,0:15:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}itu persediaan tentara. Tidak dijual.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.20,0:15:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dia anggota militer, ya?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.28,0:15:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar, aku anggota militer.\NSetidaknya, aku membuatmu berpikir begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.16,0:16:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku benar-benar anggota militer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.91,0:16:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya saja, aku tak punya pangkat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Apa yang dia katakan? Siapa dia?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lorand Spoofy. Atau haruskah kupanggil...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.55,0:16:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}..., 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.01,0:16:15.84,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}{\i1}Nama asliku?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.84,0:16:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Agar bisa mengelabui\Nbatas usia minimal untuk menjadi tentara,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.81,0:16:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau mencuri identitas seorang pria tua\Ndari kampung halamanmu, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.27,0:16:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau memang hebat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.35,0:16:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ironis, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penyamaranmu terungkap karena kau\Nbertemu lagi dengan teman lamamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.03,0:16:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Zaman sekarang, memakai identitas palsu\Nakan membuat orang mengira kau mata-mata.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.20,0:16:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Kau anggota polisi militer?\N- Bukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.33,0:16:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku anggota Badan Intelijen Militer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.12,0:16:43.41,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Aku datang untuk merekrutmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.96,0:16:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau pria yang terampil, Sersan Spoofy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.13,0:16:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada senjata yang lebih cocok untukmu\Ndibanding senapan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.51,0:16:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kecerdasan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itulah hal paling kuat dan penting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.09,0:16:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita hidup di zaman saat negara-negara
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:17:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tak bisa ambil posisi bertarung\Nsebelum dapat informasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.81,0:17:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami selalu kekurangan staf.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.06,0:17:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maukah kau bekerja untuk kami?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.27,0:17:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lebih tepatnya, sebaiknya kau setuju,\Natau akan kubawa ke pengadilan militer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau kau membantu kami
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.24,0:17:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}demi memenangkan perang ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.74,0:17:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pada hari Selasa pukul 12.00,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.95,0:17:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}berkemaslah dan pergi ke stasiun selatan\Ndengan pakaian biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.12,0:17:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan memberi tahu atasanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.84,0:17:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Meski aku mendapat senjata baru,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}itu tak akan bisa mengembalikan mereka.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.93,0:17:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Apa pun yang kulakukan,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.89,0:17:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}tak ada yang bisa membawaku\Nkembali ke masa itu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.40,0:17:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tidak akan pernah bisa...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.87,0:18:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mata-mata asli, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.17,0:18:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Komandan pasukanku\Ntak menanyakan apa pun soal kepindahanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.46,0:18:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tak memercayaiku?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.42,0:18:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak masalah. Bersikap skeptis itu bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.76,0:18:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tugas kita adalah
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.26,0:18:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bersikap skeptis terhadap semua hal,\Nentah baik atau buruk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.43,0:18:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bawa semua barang dari barakmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.68,0:18:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Ya\N- Berikan padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.31,0:18:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.94,0:18:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sersan Spoofy... Atau lebih tepatnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.23,0:18:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mulai sekarang, buanglah nama dan statusmu
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.78,0:18:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}untuk bekerja dalam bayang-bayang\Ndemi negara ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.32,0:18:43.12,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Lagi pula, sudah tak ada
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.32,0:18:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang mengenal nama itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.12,0:18:44.24,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Aku tak peduli.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,0:18:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu, aku tak cukup peduli\Nuntuk melakukan sesuatu demi negara ini
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.21,0:18:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}atau memenangkan perang ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.67,0:18:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, apa alasanmu melakukannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.42,0:18:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.84,0:18:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu, Teman-Teman!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.76,0:19:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada alasan khusus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.23,0:19:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ikuti aku, Pembohong Kecil.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.82,0:19:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku atasan barumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.82,0:19:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku diminta memberimu
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.49,0:19:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}latihan ketat agar kau\Nmenjadi agen berkualitas tinggi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, bersiaplah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.21,0:19:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah, Loid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.46,0:19:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau gelisah saat tidur.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.92,0:19:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Di mana aku?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.80,0:19:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Ini rumah Loid.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.26,0:19:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Entah kenapa,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.93,0:19:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}sepertinya aku melihat bayangan\Ndari masa lampau.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.64,0:19:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Yang melibatkan darah, debu,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.31,0:19:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}serta aroma asap senjata api...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.31,0:19:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayah bermimpi buruk?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.23,0:19:59.15,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Tidak, aku tak ingat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah. Tidak apa-apa. Jangan takut.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.74,0:20:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hentikan. Ini bukan apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.16,0:20:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, kenapa aku berada di sofa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anya pulang membawa Petir Tonitrus,\Nlalu Ayah pingsan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.38,0:20:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayah seperti iblis!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.55,0:20:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bahkan belum memarahimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.47,0:20:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Benar. Ini bisa mengacaukan Operasi Strix.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.64,0:20:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anya memang anak nakal. Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.90,0:20:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau berteman dengan Damian, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.86,0:20:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Rencana B berjalan dengan lancar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.91,0:20:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Baguslah.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.79,0:20:54.54,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Kau harus menghargai teman-temanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.51,0:21:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Haruskah kita mempersiapkan makan malam?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.51,0:21:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya. Kurasa ada sisa bawang bombai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.43,0:21:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memasak apa, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.52,0:21:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sup! Sup panas!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.55,0:21:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan pernah makan ini, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.56,0:21:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebagai gantinya,\Nakan kubuatkan jamuan besar.
